EXTRACTED VALUE: An outstanding next-gen racer and one of the best games for the 360 to date.
Level-headed and broad-minded, an excellent driving package that's as great as you make it. [July 2007, p.64]
New maps, new modes and new characters are all a feasible option with the Live service. Let’s hope they do it.
The best game currently out for the 360 and one of the best fighting games ever made.
If you’re in the market for a fun racing game that’ll keep you busy for quite some time, this is your game.
